这是 KISS 人类最后一场演出的内容https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-what-went-down-at-kiss-final-ever-show-as- humans-3553132?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=heres-what-went-低头接吻最终表演人类Alex RigottiMon, 04 Dec 2023 16:22:44 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3553132 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Kiss-Band.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Kiss 的最后一场演出（摄影：Kevin Mazur/Getty Images for Live Nation）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Kiss-Band.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Kiss-Band-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Kiss-Band-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Kiss-Band-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Kiss-Band-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Kiss-Band-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队在麦迪逊广场花园举行了最后一场演出，并透露了他们作为虚拟化身的未来</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-what-went-down-at-kiss-final-ever-show-as-humans-3553132">以下是 KISS 的最后一场演出中人类</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上的内容。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Kiss-Band.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Kiss 的最后一场演出（摄影：Kevin Mazur/Getty Images for Live Nation）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Kiss-Band.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Kiss-Band-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Kiss-Band-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Kiss-Band-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Kiss-Band-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Kiss-Band-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kiss">KISS</a>在麦迪逊广场花园表演了他们作为人类的最后一场演出 - 今晚是这样度过的。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/download-festival-2022-kiss-iron-maiden-sleep-token-wargasm-biffy-clyro-3246541">下载 Festival 2022 回顾：金属可怕的能量在较小的舞台上肆虐</a></strong></li></ul><p>乐队开始了他们的“End of the Road”告别巡演的最后一场演出，他们宣布这将是他们以人类形式乐队的最后一次演出。 KISS 相反宣布，他们将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kiss-announce-new-era-as-a-virtual-band-3552477">在节目结束时继续以虚拟化身的身份</a>——请阅读下文，了解有关麦迪逊广场花园事件的更多详细信息。</p><p>当巨大的幕布落下，乐队在屋顶巨大的悬挂平台上演奏时，KISS 以“底特律摇滚城”拉开了夜晚的序幕。</p><p>随后，乐队为歌迷带来了许多令人瞠目结舌的时刻；<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gene-simmons">吉恩·西蒙斯</a>在表演“我爱大声”时喷出了火焰。与此同时，贝斯手在《Makin&#39; Love》的独奏中也吐血了，吉他手托米·塞耶(Thommy Thayer)和主唱保罗·斯坦利(Paul Stanley)互相对决。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="KISS 登上最终音乐会舞台 + 完成《底特律摇滚城》（12/2/23 麦迪逊广场花园）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vLnCDloVCrw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="KISS - 我爱大声 - 麦迪逊广场花园 - 纽约，纽约 - 2023 年 12 月 2 日" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jELH71Wj-Xo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p></p><figure id="attachment_3553159" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3553159" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3553159" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Paul-Stanley.jpg" alt="Kiss 乐队的保罗·斯坦利（Kevin Mazur/Getty Images for Live Nation 拍摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Paul-Stanley.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Paul-Stanley-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Paul-Stanley-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Paul-Stanley-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Paul-Stanley-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Paul-Stanley-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3553159" class="wp-caption-text"> Kiss 乐队的保罗·斯坦利（Kevin Mazur/Getty Images for Live Nation 拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>当晚，斯坦利还绕着巨大的人群滑行到另一个舞台，在那里他表演了《I Was Made For Lovin&#39; You》和《Black Diamond》。</p><p>当晚最震撼的是加演环节，KISS 演奏了三首歌。他们从《Beth》开始，鼓手埃里克·辛格（Eric Singer）坐在三角钢琴上，在舞台上方演唱这首歌。然后，乐队表演了“Do You Love Me”，最后随着从体育场顶部倾泻而下的气球流结束。</p><p>但当晚最大的惊喜却是“Rock and Roll All Nite”。不仅有经典的烟火和烟火表演（以及斯坦利的吉他演奏），他还以这样的方式结束了整个夜晚：“我们不会去任何地方，你会一直在各种不同的事物中看到我们。在梦里见到你。我们爱你，晚安。”</p><p>四重奏走下舞台，迎来了新的 KISS 时代：虚拟乐队。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="KISS Final Concert Ever--FINALE 完成 ROCK &amp; ROLL ALL NITE &amp; Final KISS Goodbyes @12/2/23 MSG NYC" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/XakeY_TgZsY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Kiss Avatar 公告 - 纽约决赛" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sLQjnVNVe3w?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p></p><p>最后，当晚在乐队虚拟化身的《上帝赐予摇滚给你II》中真正结束。这些头像是由乔治·卢卡斯的特效公司 Industrial Light &amp; Magic 制作的。它们也是与 Pophouse Entertainment Group 合作制作的，该集团由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/abba">ABBA 的</a>Björn Ulvaeus 共同创立。</p><p>查看下面的完整歌单以及当晚的照片：</p><h3><strong>设置列表：</strong></h3><p><strong>底特律摇滚城</strong><br /><strong>大声喊出来</strong><br /><strong>平局</strong><br /><strong>战争机器</strong><br /><strong>天堂着火了</strong><br /><strong>我喜欢它响亮</strong><br /><strong>说耶</strong><br /><strong>冷杜松子酒</strong><br /><strong>吉他独奏</strong><br /><strong>舔起来</strong><br /><strong>打电话给爱博士</strong><br /><strong>做爱</strong><br /><strong>心理马戏团</strong><br /><strong>鼓独奏</strong><br /><strong>10万年</strong><br /><strong>低音独奏</strong><br /><strong>雷电之神</strong><br /><strong>爱枪</strong><br /><strong>我为爱你而生</strong><br /><strong>黑钻石</strong><br /><strong>安可：</strong><br /><strong>贝丝</strong><br /><strong>你爱我吗</strong><br /><strong>摇滚乐通宵</strong><br /><strong>（上帝赐予摇滚乐 II — 由 KISS 化身表演）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3553161" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3553161" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3553161" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Kiss-Band-2023.jpg" alt="吻（Kevin Mazur/Getty Images for Live Nation 拍摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Kiss-Band-2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Kiss-Band-2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Kiss-Band-2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Kiss-Band-2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Kiss-Band-2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Kiss-Band-2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3553161" class="wp-caption-text">吻（Kevin Mazur/Getty Images for Live Nation 拍摄） </figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3553162" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3553162" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3553162" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Gene-Simmons.jpg" alt="吉恩·西蒙斯（Kevin Mazur/Getty Images for Live Nation 拍摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Gene-Simmons.j